TITLE: Complete Confirmation Dialog Example with Response Handling
DESCRIPTION: Full example showing how to create and handle a confirmation dialog, including processing user response and displaying toast messages based on the choice.
SOURCE: https://github.com/acode-foundation/acode-plugin-docs/blob/main/docs/ui-components/dialogs/confirm.md#2025-04-22_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
