TITLE: Complete Keyboard Plugin Example for Acode
DESCRIPTION: A comprehensive example of a plugin that utilizes the keyboard API, including listening for keyboard visibility changes and implementing custom keyboard shortcuts.
SOURCE: https://github.com/acode-foundation/acode-plugin-docs/blob/main/docs/utilities/keyboard.md#2025-04-22_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
class KeyboardPlugin {
		constructor() {
				const keyboard = acode.require('keyboard');

				// Add keyboard show/hide listeners
				keyboard.on('keyboardShow', () => {
						acode.alert('Keyboard shown');
				});

				keyboard.on('keyboardHide', () => {
						acode.alert('Keyboard hidden');
				});

				// Listen for Ctrl+S shortcut
				keyboard.on('key', (e) => {
						if (e.key === 's' && e.ctrlKey) {
								acode.alert('Saving file...');
						}
				});
		}
}

if (window.acode) {
		const acodePlugin = new KeyboardPlugin();
		acode.setPluginInit("keyboard-example", (baseUrl, $page, { cacheFile, cacheFileUrl }) => {
				if (!acodePlugin.initialized) {
						acodePlugin.initialized = true;
						// Initialize plugin
				}
		});
}
```

