TITLE: Removing Keyboard Event Listeners in Acode Plugins
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to add and then remove an event listener for keyboard events, which is important for cleanup to prevent memory leaks.
SOURCE: https://github.com/acode-foundation/acode-plugin-docs/blob/main/docs/utilities/keyboard.md#2025-04-22_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const keyboardCallback = () => {
		console.log('Keyboard shown');
};

// Add listener
keyboard.on('keyboardShow', keyboardCallback);

// Remove listener
keyboard.off('keyboardShow', keyboardCallback);
```

